data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This meticulously maintained 3 bed 3 bath haven is nestled on a quiet cul de sac, offering the perfect blend of serenity and convenience. The primary bedroom has dual closets, including one walk-in with compliments of a spacious primary bathroom. The eat-in kitchen walks out to a beautiful deck, perfect for coffee on a spring morning OR summertime grilling! You can enjoy the main floor laundry. The walkout finished basement has the perfect setup for entertaining and additional space to make your own. The fenced-in backyard provides lots of space and even has a small pond! This home is also within walking distance of Fort Zumwalt East High School. Home to be sold AS IS.
